Job Description 3 : 

Roles and Responsibilities

- Handle customer inquiries, resolve issues, and provide solutions via phone, email, or chat.
- Process customer requests for product information, orders, returns, and exchanges in a timely and efficient manner.
- Maintain accurate records of customer interactions using CRM software.
- Ensure high quality customer service standards at all times
- Adapt to flexible shifts to support international time zones

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Job Description 4 : 

Key Responsibilities:
- Handle inbound and outbound calls to assist and engage with customers.
- Understand customer needs and provide accurate information on products and services.
- Resolve queries, complaints, and requests with a customer-first approach.
- Promote and upsell insurance products where appropriate.
- Meet and exceed daily/weekly/monthly targets.
- Build and maintain strong customer relationships to ensure repeat business.
- Maintain records and update CRM with customer details.

Required Skills:
- Excellent communication skills (English & Hindi).
- Strong customer handling and problem-solving ability.
- Good listening skills, patience, and empathy.
- Target-driven with the ability to work under pressure.
- Basic knowledge of MS Office.

